1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,500
The Legend of Zhen Huan
Episode 28

1
00:00:06,400 --> 00:00:07,200
Isn't it fun?

2
00:00:07,700 --> 00:00:09,466
Seems like Miss is in a good mood today

3
00:00:09,903 --> 00:00:12,300
Being able to gain advantage from both sides

4
00:00:14,150 --> 00:00:14,670
Actually

5
00:00:14,900 --> 00:00:17,000
Miss need not to alert Consort Hua <br>to find out about Lay Chun

6
00:00:18,800 --> 00:00:20,000
We could've covered it at first

7
00:00:20,092 --> 00:00:23,264
other people would have suspected me.

8
00:00:23,287 --> 00:00:29,423
I'd rather be left alone.<br> She deserves it for treading on forbidden ground.

9
00:00:29,423 --> 00:00:32,888
Its understandable for Consort Hua to protect Lady Chen.

10
00:00:32,888 --> 00:00:35,120
Why did you inform Consort Wan?

11
00:00:35,161 --> 00:00:40,696
Consort Hua is having the time of her life, while Consort Wan is slowly catching up.

12
00:00:40,753 --> 00:00:46,696
Even though I am on Consort Wan's side, I'm going with the flow.

13
00:00:46,696 --> 00:00:51,494
Even though she knows that its too late to save Lady Chen,

14
00:00:51,494 --> 00:00:57,495
but perhaps when Consort Wan dominates the palace one day,

15
00:00:57,554 --> 00:00:59,620
she would not put me in a difficult spot just because of what i told her today.

16
00:00:59,620 --> 00:01:03,628
Didn't Consort Wan suspect that it was Niang niang who pushed her?

17
00:01:06,294 --> 00:01:09,760
Everyone can suspect who they want. But she does not have any evidence.

18
00:01:09,794 --> 00:01:13,285
If she does, did you think I can still sit here peacefully?

19
00:01:13,316 --> 00:01:19,503
Isn't that right? Its the fight of the century.

20
00:01:19,600 --> 00:01:21,700
Instead of getting into trouble, its best that one finds an escape route.

21
00:01:21,800 --> 00:01:23,100
Is it right?

22
00:01:26,100 --> 00:01:27,500
Greetings your Majesty.

23
00:01:28,000 --> 00:01:31,000
I needed to finish looking through the proposals before coming over.

24
00:01:31,000 --> 00:01:32,400
Am I too late?

25
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:37,000
Its never too late as long as your heart is here. <br> I'll wait for you.

26
00:01:38,545 --> 00:01:41,615
So I will come no matter how late it is.

27
00:01:45,600 --> 00:01:48,700
Your majesty must be tired from working all day.

28
00:01:56,500 --> 00:01:58,700
How did you not know that i will be coming?

29
00:01:58,732 --> 00:02:00,224
Why did you prepare this?

30
00:02:00,600 --> 00:02:03,600
I am constantly wishing Emperor you will come here.

31
00:02:04,100 --> 00:02:05,700
So I always prepare it.

32
00:02:09,225 --> 00:02:11,667
With this kind thoughts from you,

33
00:02:12,100 --> 00:02:15,600
I would have missed you if I did not come.

34
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:20,000
It looks to me that you're in a good mood today.

35
00:02:20,078 --> 00:02:22,278
Could there be any good news?

36
00:02:22,319 --> 00:02:24,142
The war in the South east

37
00:02:24,200 --> 00:02:30,300
your bother and nephew has accomplished a great achievement.

38
00:02:30,300 --> 00:02:34,300
I have decided to grand your brother the title of First Class Duke.

39
00:02:34,431 --> 00:02:37,822
Your father's title will be ascended

40
00:02:37,822 --> 00:02:41,235
to Grand Mentor.

41
00:02:41,307 --> 00:02:45,156
While your brother's previous title of First Class Baron

42
00:02:45,156 --> 00:02:47,959
will be given to his second son, Nian Fu.

43
00:02:47,999 --> 00:02:52,794
I will then grand your mother the title of Madam of Gao Ming.

44
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:54,100
What do you think?

45
00:02:54,116 --> 00:02:55,833
Thank you your majesty.

46
00:02:56,952 --> 00:03:02,830
I was thinking about Consort Wan's sadness over the death of Lady Chen.

47
00:03:02,876 --> 00:03:04,877
To console her,

48
00:03:04,904 --> 00:03:08,349
I will ascend her father's position.

49
00:03:08,545 --> 00:03:12,618
Didn't you think that Consort Wan's father was disrespectful to you?

50
00:03:13,169 --> 00:03:15,779
I have given him his punishment.

51
00:03:15,920 --> 00:03:20,879
If you're against it, I will leave in the Conserate,

52
00:03:20,913 --> 00:03:24,948
and only raised his title as officer. What do you think? <br>

53
00:03:24,984 --> 00:03:28,558
I dare not justify against your majesty's decision.

54
00:03:28,580 --> 00:03:31,142
As long as Consort wan is happy.

55
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:35,000
Its great that you're so mature.

56
00:03:36,300 --> 00:03:39,600
You've been holding on to the title of Consort for quite some time.

57
00:03:39,653 --> 00:03:45,735
I'm planning to ascend your title after mid autumn.

58
00:03:48,827 --> 00:03:52,474
All I wish is to accompany your majesty.

59
00:03:52,500 --> 00:03:54,910
I care nothing about titles.

60
00:03:56,200 --> 00:03:59,100
Greetings to your highness.

61
00:03:59,100 --> 00:04:00,300
Raise.

62
00:04:00,302 --> 00:04:03,043
Thank you, your highness.

63
00:04:03,076 --> 00:04:06,356
Greetings to Consort Hua.

64
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:07,600
Raise.

65
00:04:07,634 --> 00:04:10,476
Thank you Consort Hua.

66
00:04:10,546 --> 00:04:14,232
What is with all of you today?

67
00:04:14,232 --> 00:04:20,352
As close sisters,it is only natural for us to congratulate you after hearing his majesty's decision to ascend your title

68
00:04:20,427 --> 00:04:23,831
Your highness has always lived in bliss.

69
00:04:23,918 --> 00:04:28,188
Who knew that my days would come too.

70
00:04:30,231 --> 00:04:34,269
Consort Hua, what do you mean by that?

71
00:04:34,308 --> 00:04:42,866
We've congratulated you when you were granted the title of Fujin.

72
00:04:42,936 --> 00:04:47,079
You are always in control, how smart of you.

73
00:04:47,107 --> 00:04:51,587
No matter how smart I am, it can't be compared to your highness's intelligence.

74
00:04:51,625 --> 00:04:54,868
Your highness knows his majesty best.

75
00:04:54,868 --> 00:05:00,578
May I know what title will I be granted by his majesty?

76
00:05:00,578 --> 00:05:05,433
Title above Consort is Imperial Consort, while Imperial Honored Consort is even higher.

77
00:05:05,518 --> 00:05:07,947
It should be one of them.

78
00:05:07,953 --> 00:05:09,467
Niang Niang, you are wrong.

79
00:05:09,500 --> 00:05:14,000
There's the title of Empress above Imperial Hornored Consort.

80
00:05:14,100 --> 00:05:16,500
Are you saying that you're

81
00:05:16,896 --> 00:05:20,092
interested in my title of Empress?

82
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:22,600
Niang Niang, you are overthinking.

83
00:05:22,650 --> 00:05:27,167
I happen to know that the title of Imperial Hornored Consort is equivalent to Empress.

84
00:05:27,217 --> 00:05:30,655
Back when Imperial hornored Consort Dong-E was alive

85
00:05:30,729 --> 00:05:35,176
Empress Bo Er Ji Jin did not even have the right to speak.

86
00:05:35,227 --> 00:05:37,256
How knowledgable of you.

87
00:05:37,400 --> 00:05:42,900
No matter how pretigious the title of Imperial Honored Consort is, it is equivalent to Empress.

88
00:05:43,058 --> 00:05:44,890
Empress will always be empress.

89
00:05:44,908 --> 00:05:49,773
Even with the Imperial Honored Consort, there can only be one mother of the nation.

90
00:05:49,773 --> 00:05:55,664
Consort Dong-E was still not recognized even after being crowned Imperial Honored Consort.

91
00:05:55,713 --> 00:05:58,958
It was never formal nor official.

92
00:05:59,100 --> 00:06:05,500
With your intelligence, surely you understand where your place lies.

93
00:06:05,575 --> 00:06:09,820
All I know is that, there will always be an outcry against justice.

94
00:06:09,900 --> 00:06:15,239
My opinions stirred up such a fuss from your higness.

95
00:06:15,239 --> 00:06:19,854
Others might have thought that your highness is frightened just

96
00:06:19,890 --> 00:06:24,133
like Imperial Honored Consort Bo Er Ji Jin.

97
00:06:24,248 --> 00:06:28,000
Its my duty as the empress to set the rules in the back palace.

98
00:06:28,100 --> 00:06:34,400
You should learn form you so that you could perhaps use it in the future.

99
00:06:34,438 --> 00:06:36,519
I will your highness's words in mind.

100
00:06:36,537 --> 00:06:42,692
I will surely fulfill my duty once I get ascended.

101
00:06:42,741 --> 00:06:46,649
So that empress could rest.

102
00:06:55,183 --> 00:06:58,186
You've been in low spirits

103
00:06:58,269 --> 00:07:01,176
ever since the passing of lady Chen.

104
00:07:01,200 --> 00:07:04,200
I'm relived that you're finally

105
00:07:04,200 --> 00:07:06,000
willing go out.

106
00:07:06,106 --> 00:07:10,106
Sister Mei could have accompanied me, but she has not recovered yet.

107
00:07:10,157 --> 00:07:13,548
Lady An is not feeling well either.

108
00:07:13,602 --> 00:07:19,010
But Consort Jing would come over and talk to me.

109
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:22,400
Consort Jin is indeed a warm hearted person.

110
00:07:24,700 --> 00:07:30,200
I gave you a white parrot, fearing that you might be bored. Do you like it?

111
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:33,400
Its really interesting, I really like it a lot.

112
00:07:37,500 --> 00:07:39,400
Reporting to your majesty.

113
00:07:39,700 --> 00:07:41,700
Officer Long Ko Do is here.

114
00:07:43,400 --> 00:07:45,700
I will be taking my leave now.

115
00:07:50,100 --> 00:07:51,300
Send him in.

116
00:07:51,400 --> 00:07:52,600
Yes.

117
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:01,500
greetings your majesty.

118
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:03,100
Uncle Long Ko Do

119
00:08:03,300 --> 00:08:04,600
rise.

120
00:08:04,700 --> 00:08:05,500
Thank you, your majesty.

121
00:08:05,503 --> 00:08:06,270
Have a seat.

122
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:13,400
Is there anything urgent

123
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:15,200
that you wish to see about?

124
00:08:15,300 --> 00:08:18,900
I have found out that the Nian Gengyao mansion in capital city

125
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:21,100
is under a huge renovation.

126
00:08:21,100 --> 00:08:26,600
The houses of others around it were also demolished for the sake of a garden.

127
00:08:26,623 --> 00:08:31,342
His mansion as big as Prince's estate.

128
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:39,200
I've just rewarded him. Its normal that he renovates his home extravagantly.

129
00:08:39,222 --> 00:08:43,832
Because Nian Gengyao's action, the people around him has lost their homes.

130
00:08:43,900 --> 00:08:45,900
Many of them are left homeless.

131
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:49,300
Now that he is in capital city, back in Qing Hai

132
00:08:49,400 --> 00:08:53,900
who knows, General Nian's house might get even bigger than prince's estate.

133
00:08:54,000 --> 00:08:55,700
Your taking this too seriously.

134
00:08:56,600 --> 00:08:59,000
Although Nain Geng Yao is arrogant,

135
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:01,600
he is a man who knows his place.

136
00:09:01,700 --> 00:09:02,400
Your majesty,

137
00:09:02,500 --> 00:09:05,500
Uncle and Nian Geng Yao have never gotten along.

138
00:09:05,504 --> 00:09:08,959
Niang Geng Yao was born as a servant.

139
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:12,100
Even though you're my uncle,

140
00:09:12,800 --> 00:09:17,000
there are a lot of things that I need to learn from you.

141
00:09:17,500 --> 00:09:19,500
Perhaps its because of your presence,

142
00:09:19,576 --> 00:09:23,351
that Nian Geng Yao would not dare to be overboard.

143
00:09:23,600 --> 00:09:25,200
I will never forget,

144
00:09:25,800 --> 00:09:28,400
your majesty's kindness.

145
00:09:29,400 --> 00:09:32,900
I heard that Empress Dowager is not feeling well.

146
00:09:32,915 --> 00:09:34,957
Has she gotten any better?

147
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:37,800
I would like to greet her highness.

148
00:09:37,838 --> 00:09:39,996
You must be tired from travelling,

149
00:09:40,069 --> 00:09:42,949
now that mother is sick

150
00:09:43,100 --> 00:09:46,900
if not she could have a conversation with uncle.

151
00:09:47,900 --> 00:09:49,900
Imperial doctors said that she needs to rest.

152
00:09:49,939 --> 00:09:52,224
Perhaps now is not a suitable time to meet her.

153
00:09:53,000 --> 00:09:58,500
How about paying her a visit when she gets better?

154
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:03,300
Your servant will take his leave now.

155
00:10:13,800 --> 00:10:14,100
Look.

156
00:10:15,200 --> 00:10:16,700
Your sewing is getting better.

157
00:10:16,728 --> 00:10:19,192
These flowers that you sew are looking very realistic.

158
00:10:19,700 --> 00:10:21,300
You're teasing me again.

159
00:10:21,400 --> 00:10:25,300
I was never good at sewing in the past. I only started getting better at it when I entered the palace.

160
00:10:25,700 --> 00:10:29,200
This belly band is full of a mother's love.

161
00:10:29,216 --> 00:10:31,223
It is naturally the best.

162
00:10:34,800 --> 00:10:36,900
Miss, Consort Jing,

163
00:10:36,900 --> 00:10:40,600
Servants from the palace reported that the empress is having a severe headache and is feeling very comfortable.

164
00:10:40,800 --> 00:10:43,600
Please proceed to the palace if you're free.

165
00:10:44,100 --> 00:10:46,200
Who is serving her at the moment?

166
00:10:46,300 --> 00:10:48,900
Consort Hua is with the emperor.

167
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:52,600
Lady Fucha just had a miscarriage, Lady Hui and Lady an are still ill.

168
00:10:52,800 --> 00:10:56,400
Consort Qi and Lady Xin are serving her now.

169
00:10:56,600 --> 00:10:59,000
Alright, I'm going now.

170
00:10:59,400 --> 00:11:00,900
I shall go along with you.

171
00:11:00,918 --> 00:11:02,956
Stay here if you're not feeling well.

172
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:07,400
Empress seldom feels uncomfortable, I will feel bad for not serving her.

173
00:11:07,500 --> 00:11:08,900
I shall go with you.

174
00:11:08,952 --> 00:11:10,080
alright then.

175
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:12,300
Your highness.

176
00:11:17,800 --> 00:11:20,300
Please stay strong.

177
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:31,400
Please hang in there your higness.

178
00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:35,900
Jian qiu

179
00:11:39,700 --> 00:11:41,700
Is the imperial doctor here yet?

180
00:11:41,800 --> 00:11:42,600
Not yet.

181
00:11:42,700 --> 00:11:45,900
Why didn't you cal for the imperial doctor earlier?

182
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:50,300
Its not that I didn't, but the imperial doctors on duty are not around.

183
00:11:50,303 --> 00:11:51,964
Why?

184
00:11:51,977 --> 00:11:55,798
I've asked them earlier, besides the doctors taking care of

185
00:11:55,900 --> 00:11:58,300
Empress Dowager, that can't be disturbed.

186
00:11:58,800 --> 00:12:02,400
The rest were all taken by General Nian.

187
00:12:02,402 --> 00:12:04,671
How did things turn out like this?

188
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:08,600
Heard that General Nian's is down with a serious illness,

189
00:12:08,800 --> 00:12:10,900
he took all the imperial doctors with him this afternoon

190
00:12:10,948 --> 00:12:13,620
to take care of his wife.

191
00:12:14,700 --> 00:12:16,500
How could he act this way?

192
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:19,800
This is way too ridiculous.

193
00:12:19,900 --> 00:12:23,700
How can the empress of the nation not have an imperial doctor?

194
00:12:23,800 --> 00:12:26,400
How can they all be at the minister's mansion.

195
00:12:26,500 --> 00:12:27,000
Your highness.

196
00:12:27,100 --> 00:12:28,100
Send someone

197
00:12:28,200 --> 00:12:30,100
to bring back those imperial doctors.

198
00:12:30,200 --> 00:12:31,800
I did.

199
00:12:32,000 --> 00:12:35,400
But General Nian says that his wife is in need of them.

200
00:12:35,800 --> 00:12:40,700
He even said that the imperial doctors are not to return until his wife has recovered.

201
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:44,900
Did you inform the Emperor about this?

202
00:12:44,951 --> 00:12:47,210
Her highness ordered to not alert his majesty.

203
00:12:47,300 --> 00:12:51,200
Besides...no one would dare disturb him while he is at Consort Hua's place.

204
00:12:51,300 --> 00:12:52,900
Why didn't you inform the emperor

205
00:12:52,942 --> 00:12:55,175
when she is not feeling well?

206
00:12:55,300 --> 00:12:56,000
I...

207
00:12:56,100 --> 00:12:58,500
What are waiting for?

208
00:12:58,600 --> 00:13:01,500
Go!

209
00:13:01,600 --> 00:13:05,000
Don't go, its late. The emperor needs his rest.

210
00:13:05,001 --> 00:13:09,953
Or else he'll be too tired tomorrow to handle his work.

211
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:12,200
But the imperial doctors must at least be called over.

212
00:13:12,242 --> 00:13:15,712
Its normal for the imperial doctors to be Nian's mansion.

213
00:13:15,800 --> 00:13:21,200
The gates are all closed now, I don't wish to create anymore problems.

214
00:13:21,500 --> 00:13:26,000
The imperial doctors will be back by tomorrow morning.

215
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:26,800
Your highness.

216
00:13:26,800 --> 00:13:30,100
Enough, that's it.

217
00:13:39,200 --> 00:13:40,700
Madam,

218
00:13:53,000 --> 00:13:55,300
empress was sick again last night.

219
00:13:55,316 --> 00:13:57,645
She suffered through the night because of her headache.

220
00:13:57,669 --> 00:14:00,068
So it is true.

221
00:14:00,100 --> 00:14:02,500
I'll go over later

222
00:14:02,600 --> 00:14:04,400
to greet her highness.

223
00:14:04,500 --> 00:14:07,700
Brother is too much this time. How could he have taken all the imperial doctors?

224
00:14:07,800 --> 00:14:10,000
What if there's a sudden order by the emperor?

225
00:14:10,900 --> 00:14:12,600
Send my words out.

226
00:14:12,700 --> 00:14:15,500
Tell them to send the imperial doctors who are done with their work back.

227
00:14:15,700 --> 00:14:17,000
Yes.

228
00:14:17,100 --> 00:14:17,800
Wait...

229
00:14:17,821 --> 00:14:18,537
Wait.

230
00:14:18,600 --> 00:14:21,600
Come and take a look at the emperor's breakfast with me.

231
00:14:25,000 --> 00:14:28,000
The emperor likes pickles, put it in front.

232
00:14:28,100 --> 00:14:28,900
Yes.

233
00:14:32,700 --> 00:14:34,000
Wait.

234
00:14:34,100 --> 00:14:39,600
Emperor only had a few bites of these buns yesterday, he must be bored of them. Put it further away.

235
00:14:41,400 --> 00:14:43,100
Reporting to Madam

236
00:14:43,400 --> 00:14:45,700
The eunuch from the Imperial Household is here.

237
00:14:46,000 --> 00:14:48,900
What brings him here so early in the morning?

238
00:14:49,200 --> 00:14:51,000
Bring them in.

239
00:14:51,033 --> 00:14:51,872
Yes.

240
00:14:58,200 --> 00:15:01,400
Greetings to Consort Hua.

241
00:15:05,000 --> 00:15:09,100
Isn't this the attire of an Imperial Honored Consort?

242
00:15:09,600 --> 00:15:11,200
Who ordered you to send them here?

243
00:15:11,300 --> 00:15:14,300
Your servants are just carrying out orders from our superior.

244
00:15:15,600 --> 00:15:17,300
Could it be from the Emperor?

245
00:15:17,600 --> 00:15:18,900
Your servant does not know.

246
00:15:18,900 --> 00:15:22,000
Who would dare to send out such an order other than the emperor?

247
00:15:26,700 --> 00:15:29,400
Both of you have worked hard.

248
00:15:29,400 --> 00:15:30,900
Please follow Eunuch Zhou to redeem your rewards.

249
00:15:30,946 --> 00:15:32,134
Thank you Madam.

250
00:15:32,400 --> 00:15:33,100
Yes.

251
00:15:33,200 --> 00:15:34,400
This way please.

252
00:15:36,000 --> 00:15:38,900
Congratulations Imperial Honored Consort.

253
00:15:53,700 --> 00:15:57,400
Your majesty, I have issues to report to you.

254
00:15:57,700 --> 00:15:58,600
Go ahead.

255
00:15:58,800 --> 00:16:02,400
I heard that there was no imperial doctor attending to empress's headache last night.

