00:33:38,097 --> 00:33:44,268
that there are no Oleander tress in the area where Sister Wan is living. Or else it will be bad for

513
00:33:44,289 --> 00:33:46,688
her since she is pregnant now.

514
00:33:46,688 --> 00:33:50,154
How bad is it? <br> Oleander

515
00:33:50,222 --> 00:33:54,231
is bad for pregnancy. Back in my home town, pregnant women stay away from it.

516
00:33:57,813 --> 00:34:00,561
Miss,

517
00:34:00,648 --> 00:34:03,630
its almost time to greet the empress.

518
00:34:03,690 --> 00:34:06,684
Let's hurry along. <br> I will be taking my leave now.

519
00:34:21,647 --> 00:34:25,322
Look how thick my waist is.

520
00:34:25,353 --> 00:34:27,885
I've gained a lot of weight too.

521
00:34:27,888 --> 00:34:32,624
Take a seat quickly. What's with all the weight?

522
00:34:32,691 --> 00:34:36,156
Your baby is not even 4 months old.

523
00:34:36,156 --> 00:34:39,591
Others may not see it, but I do know that this baby in my belly

524
00:34:39,630 --> 00:34:44,430
is growing day by day. <br> Indeed, its summer already.

525
00:34:47,488 --> 00:34:50,023
I remember Chun-Er,

526
00:34:50,023 --> 00:34:54,228
liked Phoenxi flowers a lot.

527
00:34:54,228 --> 00:34:57,555
I went to Bao Hua temple earlier on,

528
00:34:57,598 --> 00:35:01,494
to pray for Lady Chun.

529
00:35:01,522 --> 00:35:03,921
Its too bad that I'm pregnant,

530
00:35:04,689 --> 00:35:07,091
or else I would have personally give her my blessings.

531
00:35:07,091 --> 00:35:11,971
So that I could take revenge on her behalf.<br> Now that you're pregnant, how can you say such words?

532
00:35:13,022 --> 00:35:15,242
It will be bad if the baby hears it.

533
00:35:15,296 --> 00:35:19,334
Your throat has not recovered.

534
00:35:19,352 --> 00:35:22,251
It will be bad if you catch a cold on the way.

535
00:35:22,330 --> 00:35:26,167
I'm alright.

536
00:35:26,244 --> 00:35:31,556
I'm feeling better after talking to you. <br> Speaking of which,

537
00:35:31,556 --> 00:35:35,097
I've been feeling unwell lately.<br> Didn't Imperial doctor Zhang

538
00:35:35,133 --> 00:35:40,554
prescribe you some Ramulus soup? Ramulus can help in smoothing your throat.

539
00:35:40,627 --> 00:35:43,922
Its the best for calming down.<br> I've been drinking it everyday.

540
00:35:47,843 --> 00:35:50,622
Miss,

541
00:35:50,669 --> 00:35:53,495
Consort Qi has send someone over.

542
00:35:53,581 --> 00:35:56,552
Exactly.

543
00:36:04,226 --> 00:36:06,634
Greetings to Consort Wan

544
00:36:06,687 --> 00:36:08,844
and Lady An.<br> Rise.

545
00:36:08,897 --> 00:36:14,103
Yes madam. Consort Qi made some chestnut cake and had me send them over.

546
00:36:14,159 --> 00:36:16,644
Please have a try Consort Wan.<br> Thank madam on my behalf.

547
00:36:27,095 --> 00:36:29,231
Your servant will be taking her leave now.

548
00:36:34,687 --> 00:36:38,196
This came just in time.

549
00:36:38,220 --> 00:36:44,493
Ling-Rong, have a try. The best snacks from the Qi Feng palace, I wonder how

550
00:36:44,510 --> 00:36:47,259
would Consort Qi's snacks taste.

551
00:36:47,325 --> 00:36:51,022
Wait. Don't eat this.

552
00:36:51,124 --> 00:36:56,135
Why?

553
00:36:56,155 --> 00:37:00,687
Chestnut Cake should taste sweet. <br> Why do I smell a tinge of bitterness?

554
00:37:12,556 --> 00:37:14,558
Put it down.

555
00:37:14,673 --> 00:37:18,687
This snack has Oleander

556
00:37:18,750 --> 00:37:24,623
fluid in it. <br> This... <br> Oleander is poisonous.

557
00:37:24,692 --> 00:37:28,686
It helps in removing stasis. But everyone know that your chest has been feeling stuffy lately.

558
00:37:31,912 --> 00:37:35,905
Matching Oleander and Ramulus,

559
00:37:35,905 --> 00:37:39,038
brings great effect for removing stasis. Its bad for your pregnancy.

560
00:37:41,960 --> 00:37:46,087
The palace maid said that this was made by Consort Qi just now?

561
00:37:46,108 --> 00:37:51,823
Yes. Consort Qi must have been jealous of you being favored and pregnant.

562
00:37:51,860 --> 00:37:56,286
That's why she did this.<br> I must let the emperor know about this.

563
00:37:56,323 --> 00:37:59,568
Please be seated.

564
00:38:00,754 --> 00:38:07,728
If the emperor knows about this, he will be mad at Consort Qi.

565
00:38:07,762 --> 00:38:12,361
As the eldest son of the empress, her highness would protect 3rd prince.

566
00:38:12,438 --> 00:38:18,562
Even though she cares nothing for Consort Qi. 3rd prince is also the eldest, once he takes the throne,

567
00:38:18,623 --> 00:38:22,956
he'll definitely give you a hard time. How are you going to survive then?

568
00:38:25,224 --> 00:38:27,756
I can't let go of this easily.

569
00:38:32,315 --> 00:38:36,902
Bring these to Imperial Doctor Zhang.

570
00:38:36,987 --> 00:38:39,754
I'll make my decision later.<br> Take it away Liu-Zhu.

571
00:38:50,791 --> 00:38:54,453
Have you send the snacks Consort Wan?

572
00:38:54,555 --> 00:39:00,083
Yes, I could stay long enough

573
00:39:00,161 --> 00:39:05,419
to see Consort Wan finish it. <br> Strange... the effect should have taken place by now.

574
00:39:05,489 --> 00:39:08,298
Could I have added

575
00:39:08,298 --> 00:39:11,021
too little of it? <br> Don't be anxious Madam, lets wait a little longer.

576
00:39:15,184 --> 00:39:17,181
Greetings

577
00:39:17,290 --> 00:39:23,219
Consort Qi<br> Excused. <br> Madam, empress has summoned you

578
00:39:23,263 --> 00:39:29,761
to the palace of great benevolence. <br> The empress should be taking her afternoon nap now.

579
00:39:29,831 --> 00:39:35,100
What's the matter? <br> There must be something urgent for sure.

580
00:39:47,336 --> 00:39:49,692
Greetings your highness.

581
00:39:50,092 --> 00:39:54,155
Why is your highness not taking a nap? Even the palace maids are not around.

582
00:39:54,170 --> 00:39:58,230
Kneel down.

										

 
 


   
 

  
   
 
 


 

										